// export const nameRegex = /^[a-zA-Z ]+$/
export const nameRegex = /^[a-zA-ZÀ-ÿ\u00f1\u00d1]+(\s*[a-zA-ZÀ-ÿ\u00f1\u00d1]*)*[a-zA-ZÀ-ÿ\u00f1\u00d1]+$/
export const dniRegex = /^[0-9]*\.?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]*$/ 
export const phoneRegex = /^\d+$/
export const mailRegex = /^[a-z0-9!#$%&'*+/=?^_`{|}~-]+(?:\.[a-z0-9!#$%&'*+/=?^_`{|}~-]+)*@(?:[a-z0-9](?:[a-z0-9-]*[a-z0-9])?\.)+[a-z0-9](?:[a-z0-9-]*[a-z0-9])?$/
export const priceRegex = /^\d+$/
